name: ROBQR-S1-27
description:
The 27th AI GAN in the ROBQR Series 1 collection.

Limited edition generative artworks created from textual ninety-character Novel AI compositions processed with machine learning algorithms Vector Quantized Generative Adversarial Network (VQGAN) and a Contrastive Language–Image Pre-training (CLIP) neural network. Textual excerpts are composed from concepts, topics and themes detailed in https://ro.uow.edu.au/theses1/853/. 

Output images are all 1200 x 1200px at 144 DPI PNG-24 in 16-bit sRGB iEC61966-2.1 format. All rescaling at 4X xBRZ 2xSaI interpolation in Affinity Photo, then LuminarNeo EnhanceAI, StructureAI and RelightAI colour grading.
